					Full Description



		Hanbo Enterprises Holdings Limited is a Hong Kong-based investment holding company principally engaged in the trading of apparel products. The Company is also engaged in the provision of supply chain management services of apparel, including the sourcing of raw materials, the design and development of products and the provision of third-party manufacturing, quality control and social compliance monitoring services. Its products are mainly exported to the United States of America (the USA).
» Full Overview of 1367.HK







