Hanbo Enterprises Holdings Limited Key Developments

Hanbo Enterprises Holdings Limited Announces Board Changes
Jul 7 17
Hanbo Enterprises Holdings Limited announced that with effect from 7 July 2017, Ms. Man Tsz Sai, Lavender resigned as the company secretary of the Company and ceased to act as an authorised representative of the Company and the authorised representative to accept service of process or notice in Hong Kong on behalf of the Company to pursue personal career development. The Board is also announced that Mr. Hon Ming Sang has been appointed as the Company Secretary, the Authorised Representative and the Process Agent with effect from 7 July 2017. He is an executive Director and a member of the Compliance Committee of the Company.


Hanbo Enterprises Holdings Limited Appoints Liu Zhijun as Executive Director
Jul 7 17
The board of Directors of Hanbo Enterprises Holdings Limited announced that Mr. Liu Zhijun has been appointed as an executive Director with effect from 7 July 2017. He has extensive experience in risk investment and management of venture capital fund guided by government.


Hanbo Enterprises Holdings Limited, Special/Extraordinary Shareholders Meeting, Jun 27, 2017
Jun 8 17
Hanbo Enterprises Holdings Limited, Special/Extraordinary Shareholders Meeting, Jun 27, 2017, at 15:00 China Standard Time. Location: Plaza 1-2, Lower Lobby Novotel Century Hong Kong, 238 Jaffe Road Hong Kong Hong Kong Agenda: To consider the capital contribution agreement.


