Company Description                    




                        Hanbo Enterprises Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, is primarily engaged in the provision of apparel supply chain management services in Hong Kong, Mainland China, and internationally. The Company acts as a one-stop solution provider by providing a wide range of services to its customers to meet their needs along the apparel supply chain. Its apparel supply chain management services include sourcing of raw materials and third-party manufactures, sample creation, product design and development, production management, merchandising, quality control, logistics management and social compliance monitoring services for woven wear, such as shirts, pants, jeans, and jackets. It also trades apparel products. The Company was incorporated in 1991 and is headquartered in Hong Kong.                     


